                <offset>0</offset>
                <text>ï»¿A non-consanguineous 31-year-old couple (II-1 and II-2) was referred to the Jikei University Hospital with a neonate at 13 weeks of gestation with severe fetal hydrops (III-2) (Figure 1a).</text>
                <annotation id="1">
                    <infon key="type">webanno.custom.Phenotypes</infon>
